Sorry doc,<br><br>
The hyena pack needs guys like me to nip at their heels to keep them in line. Oh sure, they may get a little irritated at me, but they damn sure know where I stand.<br><br>
As far as holding any ideals &quot;so high&quot;, my words are all over this website. I have invested as much time as any here. Some people on this site sound like broken records. Verbose ones at that. One no longer has to scan down to see the author's name. Certain words stand out that make the author easily recognizable. <br><br>
Quite possibly the namecalling HAS intimidated some from posting. I have consistently refrained from this activity. You fail to realize that those who defame this way are only a reflection of our society today - which, like the namecalling - shows a tendency to mediocrity. People choose whether or not to rise above being ordinary and predictable. It is reflected here.<br><br>
 But, it all boils down to this: they are only words. I still have to go out in the world each day and fend for myself. My workdays are full of cooperation with people who have radically different ideas than mine. I am extremely proud of my capacity to WORK with these people. I accomplish things everyday with these very people. One reason is that we are able to put our politics and prejudices on the shelf for a few hours. When that is done we come to realize that we are quite similar and capable of great things.<br><br>

